 Destructor walked into the mess hall and sat down with Kit Kat. He had some 
questions for her. He got completely serious...something he had trouble doing 
around her..."Why do you wish to clone our warriors? It seems the only idea 
you can have at your requsest for the replicators. I want you to think before 
you realize the dangers of what might happen" All he could think about at 
this point was what one treacherous pred could do to a team but make more of 
the same. It was not his favorite idea.
